Module foms
Package foms.workers

Class Worker

java.lang.Object
foms.workers.Worker
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
AdminWorker, StaffWorker
public class Worker extends Object implements Serializable
An abstract class that serves as the base class for all workers in the food order management system. It provides common functionality and properties for all types of workers.
